house that once was occupied by Hunter S. Thompson.  
Their mission is to extract his Gonzo powers. There 
are two places that might be suitable for the spirit 
revival, the big house, and the cabin in the woods. 
Terrorists, wanting to protect Thompson's dead ass, 
have decided to intervene.

CTs: Eliminate the threat of the terrorist team, 
then perform your spirit revivals.

Ts: Blow up the two locations so there is no chance 
the CTs can hold their spirit revivals. Killing is optional.

Hello! This is updated version of my map called de_pakkassauna. I wasn't fully satisfied with older version so I decide to make an improved one.
Some changes and features:

-HDR Lighting effect

-3D Skybox

-Improved cliffs

-New Layout focusing on better gameplay; corridors are bigger to help moving and prevent getting stuck. Less annoying ladders ;) . Terrorists have 2 new routes (basement tunnel and cottage side route). All these changes are made to improve team balance and making games more action-filled and less camping-skilled.

-Only one bombsite (it says there are A and B but they are next to each other in showerroom and sauna).

-Custom textures, custom models, more realistic details, environment sounds, working radio...

-Improved lightning

Server owners! If you are using older version of de_pakkassauna please replace older with this newer version, much better to play in servers I doubt.
And all others if you have downloaded older version and liked it I suggest you to give a try for this too!

Big thanks to all custom content makers TopHATTwaffle, Klickz72 and Dinus Saurus. You helped me to make this map better :) .
Enjoy or not, and remember to rate and comment!

This is my saunamap. I really tried to make it enjoyable. It's fast-paced defusal map what offers quick action even with 2 players. Map is good for sneaking or rushing gamestyle. Map is designed for 2-10 players LAN gaming. Map is somewhat detailed, but I'm real amateur in mapping ( experience in Hammer 6 months ).
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
MAP CONTAINS:
- A warm and nice sauna with heatwave effect
- Fog and snowflakes
- Super secret weapon room ( you have to find it yourselves )
- Telephone poles, and other "realistic" details
- Lightswitches inside cottage
- Tunnels
- A real finnish outdoor toilet :D
- 8 CT & 8 T spawnpoints
- Two bomb sites, they are both easily found and marked

Location is fictional, but it could be some around in Northern Europe.

STORYLINE:
It's cold day, winter's last snow is raining from foggy sky. Spring is soon coming. Counter-Terrorist are having beer party in the sauna. Terrorists weren't invited to party, and they became angry. As revenge terrorists decided to bomb the whole cottage, or shoot all counter-terrorists.

COUNTER-TERRORISTS:
Defend the sauna and the tunnels. You don't want to lose warm sauna and beers to terrorists, eh? Defuse the bomb, or kill all terrorists. CTs start from tunnels under cottage.

TERRORISTS: You wan't to steal ct's sauna and beers? Go ahead! Remember that victory don't come with camping. Plant the bomb to site A or B , or kill all counter-terrorists. Terrorists get 3 free smoke grenades from spawn, so they can make covering smoke to help moving. Terrorists start from gravel road near cottage.

FEEDBACK: Please rate and comment this map. Tell what could done better or should improved. Your feedback helps to make this map better.
 in public server, let me know.

ALSO READ: You need my permission first if you want to modify map. And it's not clever because I'm already fixing bugs and improving this map. If you want to use this map on server, post your server's name and adress so I can visit there and see how map works in game.

This small army outpost is under attack from local terrorist forces.
They are at the front gate and making their way over the fence 
under the cover of night.

-------------------------------------------------------------------

Ct's must neutralise the threat and protect any potential bomb targets.

-------------------------------------------------------------------

T's must storm the base and plant the bomb at one of the two 
targets, the Operations room or the Storage room containing toxic
materials.

-------------------------------------------------------------------

As well as buy zones weapons can be found on this map for
both teams, although ct's have an armoury at their disposal.

Any ct's that spawn in a Guard Tower will automatically be armed with
an M4.

NVG's are very useful on this map.

Updates: Added a minimap, fixed some of the textures not showing up online, and a few other minor things. :)

Map features:
2 strategicly located bomb sites.
32 spawn points (16 each team).
A large tunnel network.
Terrorists have 3 seperate spawn locations, Counter-Terrorists have 2.

Installation:
Extract the map file (de_outpost.bsp), and the navigation file (de_outpost.nav) to your Counter-Strike maps folder (Usually located here:C:\Program Files\steam\steamapps\***YOURNAMEHERE***\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps)

Author:
BarbaraWalters

Time:
Around 20 hours.

Contact Information:
If you enjoy the layout of the map, but would like to improve upon it yourself, either e-mail me at wcsmanyraces@gmail.com, or contact me (BarbaraWalters) on my forums located at wcsmanyraces.freeforums.org.

Notes:  Aware of some graphical glitches, as well as just plain ugly texturing on some parts.  Also, I could not manage to get HDR working correctly.  The map just had to be finished as I have other things I need to get around to doing.  Any mods/fixes are appreciated.  Also, this may seem sort of large, but the original idea is designed for my Warcraft mod server, so hopefully everyone can still enjoy.

Plot:
A massive supply of precious metals has been located deep in the heart of the Congo.  Combined government forces moved fast and established a mining outpost.  Anti Globalization Guerillas are at the facility, trying to either take out the resources, or stop the government forces backup from arriving.The workers have all either fled or been killed.  Government troops are now forced to take up defensive positions, guarding their communications equipment, and keeping the mine intact.

Enjoy!

-custom sounds
-HDR

-highly optimized with hint and portal brushes
-custom models

Thanks to Pedroleum for the crop and scarecrow models. Thanks to Ranson for the trough and milk can props. Thanks to chizbone for doing the nav. Thanks to Valve.

Enjoy

ORILLA HOUSE

Bomb/Defuse Map for Counter-Strike: Source

CS:S original map creator (cs_version): NILIX
CS:S sequel map creator (de_version): Niko
Navigation Mesh editor: Meurglis3

High quality sequel of the same-named hostage rescue map for CS:S by NILIX (originally released August 2012), reproducing the land plot near a seacoast with a spacious two-story house. This remake contains a few significant design and visual changes compared to the original source, which were made due to change of game mode for maximum gameplay smoothness.

Story:
   Eight years after the hostage-taking incident a pair of police officers tried to break into the house on a seacoast owned by a retired mobster to get documentary evidence of his past criminal activities. However the owner of the estate has not lost its former grip and was on the alert! He tried to destroy his archive, then to go on the run. But after shooting both cops, he died of his own injuries...   Now to the house on a seacoast in a hurry two teams. Police special forces will try to capture the surviving remnants of incriminating documents. And the fighters of an organized criminal group will try to destroy potential evidence: a homeowner's private archive (den at the second floor) or a contents of the safe's wreckage (kitchen at the ground floor). Who will eventually win..?

Note: In design of this map used some custom assets created by Yanzl for CS:GO maps cs_cruise and de_resort.

P.S. ~ Curiosity is ill manners in another’s house :-)
